# Sanskrit Love Concepts Extraction – Phase One

## Research Assistant Protocol Declaration

I have conducted searches for peer-reviewed scholarship on love concepts in Sanskrit philosophy. Searches returned predominantly devotional/scriptural (non-peer-reviewed) sources. Only sources explicitly verified as peer-reviewed journals, academic presses, or SEP/IEP entries are included below.

**Scholarship Status**: THIN. Multiple peer-reviewed sources mention lists of Sanskrit love terms in passing, but detailed operational extraction across the seven fields is fragmentary. Several expected peer-reviewed sources could not be verified (full articles behind paywalls; abstracts insufficient for extraction).

